---
---
<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why skillx?</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card neo-box">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <span>⏳</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-header">
          <h3>No Install Needed</h3>
          <span class="highlight-badge">ephemeral</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          Run any skill temporarily. It's fetched, injected, and auto-cleaned
          when your session ends. Nothing is permanently added to your project.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card neo-box">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <span>⊘</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-header">
          <h3>Security First</h3>
          <span class="highlight-badge">23 rules</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          Every skill is scanned across 5 risk levels before injection.
          Dangerous patterns are blocked &mdash; you never run untrusted code.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card neo-box">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <span>⚡</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-header">
          <h3>One Command</h3>
          <span class="highlight-badge">zero config</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          No setup, no config files. One command pulls from any Git host,
          scans, runs, and cleans up. That's it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: #fdf6e3;
    border-top: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translate(-4px, -4px);
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px #1a1a1a;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    background: #6366f1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #1a1a1a;
  }

  .feature-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .highlight-badge {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    background: #ff9f1c;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
